OL,5, A "very damaged man" has been jailed   
OL,6, for killing his bedbound grandfather in
OL,7, a knife attack, in the first filmed    
OL,8, sentencing in England and Wales.       
OL,10,FBen Oliver, 25, stabbed his 74-year-old
OL,11,Fgrandfather to death in Mottingham,    
OL,12,Fsouth London, in January 2021.         
OL,14,FHe admitted manslaughter due to        
OL,15,Fdiminished responsibility. He was      
OL,16,Fcleared of murder at the Old Bailey.   
OL,18,FJudge Sarah Munro QC made legal history
OL,19,Fas she handed him a life sentence with 
OL,20,Fa minimum of 10 years and eight months.
